						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the Hanumantadēva temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 13th century.</p>						

						<p>It seems to refer to the installation of the god Yādavarāya by Anantarasa in memory of his father Bommarasa.</p>						

